  "texts": [
    "It aimed to discuss how healthier food delivery initiatives may be encouraged to safeguard young adults' and society's future health.",
    "To guide this investigation, the following supporting objectives have been formulated:",
    "To explore the nutritional quality of food delivery meals consumed by young adults in Shanghai;",
    "To explore young adults' dietary habits and preferences when they use food delivery services in Shanghai;",
    "To ascertain the factors that impede healthy eating habits among young adults using food delivery services in Shanghai;"
